---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Messianic Jewish Resources - Ohr HaTorah" pageTitle="Messianic Jewish Resources for Beginners" pageIcon="fas fa-book-open">
    <p class="intro-text"><strong>Explore the rich heritage of Messianic Judaism with these trusted resources and organizations.</strong></p>

    <!-- Major Organizations -->
    <div class="resource-section">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-building"></i> Major Organizations</h3>

        <div class="resource-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-synagogue"></i> Union of Messianic Jewish Congregations (UMJC)</h4>
            <p>A network of about 70 Messianic congregations worldwide that honor Yeshua as Messiah. Provides mutual support, leadership development, and practical guidance for congregations.</p>
            <a href="https://www.umjc.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">
                Visit UMJC <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="resource-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-globe"></i> Jewish Voice Ministries</h4>
            <p>A Messianic Jewish ministry sharing the Gospel of Yeshua to Jewish people first and also to Gentiles. Offers educational resources and humanitarian aid worldwide.</p>
            <a href="https://www.jewishvoice.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">
                Visit Jewish Voice <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Educational Resources -->
    <div class="resource-section">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> Educational Resources</h3>

        <div class="resource-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-seedling"></i> First Fruits of Zion (FFOZ)</h4>
            <p>Specializes in teaching Scripture from its historical, linguistic, and cultural Jewish context. Offers Torah Club studies, books, and educational materials connecting Christians with Jewish foundations.</p>
            <a href="https://ffoz.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">
                Visit FFOZ <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="resource-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-star-of-david"></i> Chosen People Ministries</h4>
            <p>Founded in 1894, this ministry reaches Jewish people with the Gospel in 17 countries. Offers evangelism training, Passover presentations, and educational resources about Jewish evangelism.</p>
            <a href="https://chosenpeople.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">
                Visit Chosen People <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="resource-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-pray"></i> Jews for Jesus</h4>
            <p>Provides resources for Jewish holidays, Scripture study, interfaith couples, and lifecycle events. Known for creative evangelism and Jewish cultural education materials.</p>
            <a href="https://jewsforjesus.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">
                Visit Jews for Jesus <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Publishers & Books -->
    <div class="resource-section">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-book"></i> Publishers & Essential Books</h3>

        <div class="resource-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-bookmark"></i> Messianic Jewish Publishers</h4>
            <p>The only full-fledged Messianic Jewish publishing house. Publishers of the Complete Jewish Study Bible, Torah devotionals, and essential Messianic literature for beginners and scholars.</p>
            <a href="https://www.messianicjewish.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">
                Visit MJ Publishers <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="resource-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-tree"></i> Tree of Life Version Bible (TLV)</h4>
            <p>A distinctive Messianic Jewish translation highlighting the Jewish roots of faith. Created by Jewish believers and Christian scholars to restore the Jewish essence of Scripture.</p>
            <a href="https://tlvbiblesociety.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">
                Visit TLV Bible <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="resource-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-newspaper"></i> The Messianic Times</h4>
            <p>Leading international Messianic Jewish newspaper published six times yearly. Features news, articles, and perspectives from the worldwide Messianic community.</p>
            <a href="https://messianictimes.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">
                Visit Messianic Times <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="resource-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-scroll"></i> Complete Jewish Study Bible</h4>
            <p>Highly rated study Bible (4.7/5 stars) with Jewish cultural context, commentary, and notes. An excellent starting point for understanding Scripture from a Messianic Jewish perspective.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Getting Started -->
    <div class="tips-section">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Getting Started Tips</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Begin with the <strong>Complete Jewish Study Bible</strong> for foundational understanding</li>
            <li>Explore <strong>FFOZ Torah Club</strong> for small group study</li>
            <li>Connect with local congregations through <strong>UMJC</strong></li>
            <li>Subscribe to <strong>The Messianic Times</strong> for community news and insights</li>
            <li>Attend conferences and events hosted by these organizations</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</PageLayout>

<style>
    .intro-text {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .resource-section {
        margin-bottom: 35px;
    }

    .resource-section h3 {
        color: var(--primary-blue);
        border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-blue);
        padding-bottom: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .resource-card {
        background: var(--gray-100);
        padding: 20px 25px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .resource-card h4 {
        color: var(--primary-blue);
        margin: 0 0 12px 0;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .resource-card h4 i {
        margin-right: 8px;
        color: var(--gold-dark);
    }

    .resource-card p {
        margin: 0 0 15px 0;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
    }

    .resource-link {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        background: var(--primary-blue);
        color: white;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .resource-link:hover {
        background: #004080;
    }

    .tips-section {
        background: var(--gold-light);
        padding: 25px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
    }

    .tips-section h3 {
        color: var(--gold-dark);
        margin: 0 0 15px 0;
    }

    .tips-section ul {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .tips-section li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
</style>
